you always wanted your whole life.

38:01.479 --> 38:03.413
Somethin' that makes you happy.

38:03.514 --> 38:07.678
I want the money. I really do.
It's Christine, she keeps...

38:07.785 --> 38:10.276
All right. Let me worry
about Christine, okay?

38:10.388 --> 38:12.117
I'll worry about Christine.

38:12.223 --> 38:15.249
You worry about Tom,
'cause it's Tom time.

38:15.359 --> 38:19.056
- [Knocking] Christine?
- Yes, dear?

38:19.163 --> 38:22.155
- Can I talk to you?
- Of course, dear. I'm your mother.

38:22.266 --> 38:24.166
You can talk to me
about anything.

38:24.268 --> 38:25.462
Great.

38:25.569 --> 38:28.902
- Are you all right?
- Uh-huh.

38:29.006 --> 38:32.442
You sure? 'Cause you just put
a bra in Brian's sock drawer.

38:32.543 --> 38:34.170
Oh, well, that's your brother.

38:34.278 --> 38:37.338
15. Likes to experiment.
We still love him.

38:38.783 --> 38:43.686
Look, Christine, I know what's going on
with you and Tom,

38:43.788 --> 38:46.518
and first of all,
I just wanna say that

38:46.624 --> 38:49.787
I'm feeling a little ripped off here,
you know?

38:49.894 --> 38:52.727
