40:02.166 --> 40:03.394
[Sobbing]

40:03.501 --> 40:05.969
Or not.
I mean, whatever...

40:06.070 --> 40:11.064
Oh, Drew, you've made
your mama so happy.

40:11.175 --> 40:12.938
[Chuckles] Great.

40:14.678 --> 40:18.774
- Oh, Mom.
- [Christine chuckles]

40:25.055 --> 40:27.489
[Drew] Hey, Alicia.
Want to go tobogganing?

40:28.926 --> 40:32.054
Oh, I'm sorry, Drew.
Have I been sending you mixed signals?

40:32.163 --> 40:35.462
[Chuckles] I just thought
maybe instead of sitting around

40:35.566 --> 40:38.535
