you might like to have some fun.

40:38.636 --> 40:40.570
No, thanks.

40:40.671 --> 40:42.662
[Drew] Ah, I see.

40:42.773 --> 40:44.832
I get it.

40:44.942 --> 40:47.911
You're afraid of fun.
You don't like having fun.

40:48.012 --> 40:50.810
What the hell does that even mean,
"I don't like fun"?

40:50.915 --> 40:52.405
Of course I like fun.

40:52.516 --> 40:55.212
Everybody likes fun. It's fun.

40:55.319 --> 40:58.049
All right, so then why
won't you go with me?

40:58.155 --> 41:00.248
Because it would be with you.

41:00.357 --> 41:03.155
You know what I think?
I think you're afraid.

41:03.260 --> 41:06.058
I think you're afraid
that you will go, and have fun,

41:06.163 --> 41:08.723
and you might enjoy yourself,
and you'd be with me.

41:08.833 --> 41:11.393
What would that say about you?
That's what I think.

41:11.502 --> 41:13.766
- Really?
- [Drew] Mm-hm.

41:14.705 --> 41:16.536
Let's go.

41:19.076 --> 41:21.544
- [Alicia] All right.
- [Drew] Ready, Freddie.

41:21.645 --> 41:23.943
- Well, hello there, youngsters.
- Hi.

41:24.048 --> 41:25.777
- Tobogganing?
- Breakneck Hill.

41:25.883 --> 41:27.214
- Fun.
- [Drew] Yeah.

41:27.318 --> 41:28.785
