41:35.593 --> 41:37.322
[Rock music playing]

41:43.267 --> 41:44.564
What do you think?

41:44.668 --> 41:46.135
Nice.

41:46.237 --> 41:48.671
Yeah. This'll keep you
from dying, Dad.

41:48.772 --> 41:50.637
Had one of these
when I was single.

41:50.741 --> 41:52.436
I bet.

41:52.543 --> 41:54.943
