around my daughter.

42:02.119 --> 42:05.247
Brian, take a look at your father's
new automobile here!

42:05.356 --> 42:07.415
Yeah, what do you think?

42:07.525 --> 42:09.288
It's old.

42:09.393 --> 42:11.327
[Alicia] All right.
Hey, Bri, come on.

42:11.428 --> 42:15.057
- We're gonna go tobogganing.
- That's great.

42:20.204 --> 42:22.104
