42:52.736 --> 42:56.536
Isn't she sexy? Erotic.

42:56.640 --> 42:58.540
- Speak!
- Absolutely, Heinrich.

42:58.642 --> 43:01.839
- She's got that special quality...
- Get out now.

43:01.946 --> 43:05.438
- But I'm agreeing with you.
- You hesitated.

43:05.549 --> 43:08.677
Yeah, you heard him.
Get out! Beat it!

43:08.786 --> 43:11.311
Get out! Beat it!

43:11.422 --> 43:15.256
[Chuckling] Uh-oh.
He thinks we're serious.

43:15.359 --> 43:18.089
We were serious.

43:18.195 --> 43:20.561
Very serious.

43:20.664 --> 43:22.757
<i>[Warrant: She's My Cherry Pie]</i>

43:22.866 --> 43:25.027
[Heinrich] Yeah!

43:25.135 --> 43:27.763
<i>Ausgeseichnet! Yeah!</i>

43:27.871 --> 43:30.567
Yeah! Yeah!

43:30.674 --> 43:34.440
Ah! Erotic! Yeah! Yeah!

43:34.545 --> 43:35.534
Oh, yeah! Great!

43:35.646 --> 43:36.977
Oh, more!

43:37.081 --> 43:39.447
Lick the lollipop! Yeah!

43:39.617 --> 43:41.482
[Brian] I do not want to do this.

43:41.585 --> 43:43.450
Ah, you say that now.

43:43.554 --> 43:48.048
Once you get going, you'll run and jump
and squeal with joy.

43:48.692 --> 43:50.557
- [Drew] Okay?
- [Alicia] Let's do this.

43:50.661 --> 43:52.288
[Drew] Here we go.
Hunker down.

43:52.396 --> 43:55.229
Center your weight.
Breakneck Hill!

43:59.536 --> 44:02.437
Whoo! Whoo!

44:02.539 --> 44:05.440
That was crazy!
Did you see him fly down the hill?

44:06.377 --> 44:08.937
I made a mistake.
It was scarier when I was younger.

44:09.046 --> 44:11.276
- Can we go home now?
- No, we can't go home!

44:11.382 --> 44:14.874
We are gonna risk permanent paralysis
or die trying!

44:20.858 --> 44:23.884
That one! Land!

44:26.664 --> 44:30.964
[Drew] Yes, sir! Whoo!
Gonna be some serious fun!

44:31.068 --> 44:34.196
