kind of way.

44:35.606 --> 44:37.836
What's that I hear?
A little chicken?

44:37.941 --> 44:39.238
[Clucks]

44:39.343 --> 44:42.335
- Chicken.
- Yeah. And very much so.

44:42.446 --> 44:43.913
I'm gonna go home now.

44:44.014 --> 44:47.177
- Seriously? You're leaving?
- [Brian] See ya at the chopper.

44:47.284 --> 44:51.414
Wow. Never thought I'd see the day
that taunt would lose its power.

44:51.522 --> 44:53.888
What about you?
Chicken with broccoli?

44:53.991 --> 44:57.222
Actually, part of me thinks
that it's incredibly stupid,

44:57.327 --> 44:59.488
and the other part is in agreement.

44:59.596 --> 45:01.496
- There you go.
- You're chicken.

45:01.598 --> 45:03.031
- Know what I think?
- What?

45:03.133 --> 45:07.160
I think that you had no intention
of going down this hill.

45:07.271 --> 45:11.401
I think that you dragged us up here
because you knew we wouldn't go down it.

45:11.508 --> 45:14.966
I think you were showing off.
That's what I think.

45:15.079 --> 45:16.637
Wait. You think I'm chicken?

45:16.747 --> 45:18.544
- I'm chicken?
- [Alicia laughs]

45:18.649 --> 45:22.380
Let me give a little clue here, okay?

45:22.486 --> 45:25.046
You think I'm chicken?
I'll show you.

45:25.155 --> 45:26.645
You see me?
I'm ready to go.

45:26.757 --> 45:29.351
Where are you?
Nowhere to be seen. Chicken.

45:29.460 --> 45:30.950
All right.
Come on. Let's go.

45:31.061 --> 45:32.653
- You're getting on?
- Yeah.

45:32.763 --> 45:34.731
- No!
- Come on, push off.

45:34.832 --> 45:36.697
