45:59.389 --> 46:01.755
[Both screaming]

46:01.859 --> 46:04.885
[Laughing]

46:09.366 --> 46:11.834
- Oh, my God.
- Oh, God.

46:13.203 --> 46:16.434
I told you you'd have fun with me.

46:27.351 --> 46:29.683
[Sneezes]

46:29.787 --> 46:34.053
- Sorry.
- That's cool. It's okay.

46:37.561 --> 46:41.156
- Here you go.
- Thank you.

46:42.432 --> 46:45.868
- It's my fault you got sick.
- [Sniffling] It's not your fault.

46:45.969 --> 46:48.904
We even might have gotten sick
without tobogganing.

46:49.006 --> 46:51.474
It didn't help walking home
in wet clothes.

46:51.575 --> 46:55.272
- You wanna watch TV?
- Uh-huh.

46:55.379 --> 46:57.006
[Drew groaning]

47:01.652 --> 47:04.587
<i>[Warrant: She's My Cherry Pie]</i>

47:24.675 --> 47:26.870
- Hey.
- Hi.

47:31.682 --> 47:33.946
You look different.

47:34.051 --> 47:36.315
Did you do something?

47:37.588 --> 47:38.816
Are you serious?

47:38.922 --> 47:41.857
No, I just mean that...

47:43.594 --> 47:44.993
...you look good.

47:47.698 --> 47:49.256
Thanks.

47:50.601 --> 47:51.829
Where'd you go?

47:52.669 --> 47:54.330
Nice wheels.

47:55.572 --> 47:59.804
- Yeah. You like it?
- Yeah.

48:01.178 --> 48:04.079
Does it seem at all familiar?

48:05.916 --> 48:08.282
Didn't somebody we know
have one of these?

48:08.385 --> 48:11.479
Yeah. Us.

48:11.588 --> 48:14.386
Maybe this'll help.

48:18.662 --> 48:22.098
Yeah. I remember.

48:37.948 --> 48:41.509
- So what's your deal anyway?
- My deal.

48:41.618 --> 48:44.587
I mean, sometimes you have
these moments of lucidity,

48:44.688 --> 48:46.849
but then other times

48:46.957 --> 48:50.051
it's just not so much normal.

48:50.160 --> 48:54.119
I don't understand, I mean,
I don't wanna be alone on Christmas.

48:54.231 --> 48:55.823
You've never been alone.

48:55.933 --> 48:59.494
On Christmas, it's not like
being alone. It's alone alone.

48:59.603 --> 49:02.094
