52:17.234 --> 52:19.862
Hey, would you come outside
with me for one second?

52:19.970 --> 52:23.428
- I wanna show you something.
- Okay.

52:23.540 --> 52:26.031
- Where are you taking me?
- Hold on, one second.

52:26.143 --> 52:29.772
- You trust me?
- Uh, no. Not necessarily.

52:29.880 --> 52:32.440
Okay. Try to trust me,
I wanna blindfold you.

52:32.549 --> 52:34.107
- It's a surprise.
- Okay.

52:34.217 --> 52:36.583
- All right?
- All right.

52:36.686 --> 52:39.553
- Oh, God.
- All right. Follow me.

52:39.656 --> 52:44.423
