52:44.528 --> 52:46.496
- Step, step, step.
- Okay.

52:46.596 --> 52:48.029
- Right there. Stop.
- Okay.

52:48.131 --> 52:50.292
- Turn this way. Okay?
- All right.

52:50.400 --> 52:52.334
All right.

53:00.477 --> 53:03.674
[Breathless] Oh, my God.

53:06.016 --> 53:09.474
[Stammers] I can't believe you did this.

53:09.586 --> 53:11.383
Wait till you see this.

53:11.488 --> 53:12.819
Hit it, guys.

53:12.923 --> 53:17.053
[Elves] Hut, hut, hut...

53:21.598 --> 53:26.763
- [elves giggling]
- [Camel grunts]

53:30.574 --> 53:33.839
[Donkey brays]

53:33.944 --> 53:35.206
You see that?

53:35.312 --> 53:37.780
That's you right there.
I know this props guy.

53:37.881 --> 53:39.678
He owns a prop house with figurines,

53:39.783 --> 53:42.308
and he painted your hair like that,
your mouth.

53:42.419 --> 53:44.410
- Those guys aren't pros.
- I'm sure.

53:44.521 --> 53:46.955
- I showed them the thing.
- Oh, wow.

53:47.057 --> 53:50.390
I got this dance teacher.
It's not easy to get a camel.

53:50.493 --> 53:54.725
It's not easy taking a very
personal and private moment

53:54.831 --> 53:58.528
that I have never told anybody
and turning it into a theme park.

53:58.635 --> 54:00.432
<i>We wish you a Merry Christmas</i>

54:00.537 --> 54:01.868
Shut up!

54:01.972 --> 54:03.872
[Choir] Ah...

54:03.974 --> 54:06.966
But I'm not disappointed.
Okay? I'm not mad.

54:07.077 --> 54:11.946
I'm just mad at myself for thinking that
there was more to you than I thought.

54:13.216 --> 54:15.844
- That's you.
- [Man] It's a wrap.

54:15.952 --> 54:17.852
[Elves] Hut, hut, hut.

54:17.954 --> 54:19.615
[Drew] Alicia? Wait a second!

54:19.723 --> 54:23.557
I care about you.
I did that because I care about you.

54:23.660 --> 54:26.026
Look, Drew,
let me just give you some advice.

54:26.129 --> 54:28.495
Save your big, expensive gestures

54:28.598 --> 54:30.793
for some girl
who's impressed by them,

54:30.900 --> 54:33.027
