a lifetime of lonely Christmases.

54:45.548 --> 54:49.040
I'm telling you, he is wonderful.

54:49.152 --> 54:51.620
It's Cartier.
At least he's got manners.

54:51.721 --> 54:53.848
Well, I mean,
he's in the neighborhood.

54:53.957 --> 54:55.424
- He is?
