55:13.109 --> 55:16.135
Brian, tell Drew
that I had to take off.

55:16.246 --> 55:17.975
There was a...

55:21.885 --> 55:24.615
Holy cow.
What are you looking at?

55:24.721 --> 55:28.452
This is just, it's research.

55:28.558 --> 55:30.719
When I was young,
we didn't sit in our rooms

55:30.827 --> 55:33.159
drooling over nude ladies
on computers.

55:33.263 --> 55:34.730
No, sir.

55:34.831 --> 55:37.129
