with the dirty girl

55:37.233 --> 55:40.964
and pay her a quarter so she
could show us her goodies.

55:42.238 --> 55:43.569
How does this work?

55:43.673 --> 55:47.404
Oh, well. Here, let me...

55:47.510 --> 55:50.206
[Brian] What are you into?
Hot Cheerleaders,

55:50.313 --> 55:52.076
- Three-Way Fun.
- Uh-uh.

55:52.182 --> 55:54.946
- Middle-Aged Hotties.
