56:02.592 --> 56:04.287
[Doo-Dah] Come to papa.

56:04.394 --> 56:06.624
[Brian] That's not bad, right?

56:09.666 --> 56:12.294
Dude, it's your mom!

56:12.402 --> 56:13.528
Oh, my God.

56:15.004 --> 56:17.370
Hey, can you print that for me?

56:18.975 --> 56:20.772
Mom, Dad, listen.

56:20.877 --> 56:22.469
Please, Drew has to go tonight.

56:22.579 --> 56:25.377
I cannot spend one more second
in this house with him.

56:25.482 --> 56:27.575
- Well, yeah?
- Yeah? So what?

56:27.684 --> 56:30.084
So he's making fools of us!

56:30.186 --> 56:31.915
- Of all of us!
- [Drew] Alicia?

56:32.021 --> 56:34.819
[Sighs] All right, look,
I'm gonna take the car,

56:34.924 --> 56:37.256
